Package: ineqstats
Type: Package
Title: Simple Inequality Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Marijana", "Malic",
      email = "malic.marijana@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tools to compute inequality measures like the Gini coefficient, Lorenz curve,
              calculates the share of total income held by the top p proportion and
              provides some summary statistics (median, mean, min, max, variance)
              for the given data.
